# macOS
.DS_Store

# Internal design/brainstorm docs (kept locally, not published)
docs/superpowers/
BACKLOG.md

# Logs (the routine writes to ~/Library/Logs, but ignore any stray local logs)
*.log

# Config/secrets: the real .env (with webhook URLs) lives in
